Organization Name: Home Dialysis Therapies of San Diego
Description: Advanced kidney disease to be independent and provide comprehensive and compassionate care that will help you live life to the fullest.
Headquarters Regions: Greater San Diego Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Dialysis is a treatment that replaces some of the work normally done by the kidneys. This includes balancing fluid, balancing electrolytes and removing waste products from your blood. Several dialysis treatment options are available for people with advanced chronic kidney failure, also called end stage renal disease (ESRD) or Stage 5 Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD). Peritoneal dialysis is a type of dialysis that uses your peritoneal membrane as a filter to clean your blood. The peritoneal membrane is a natural filter that surrounds your abdominal cavity. With this type of dialysis, sterile dialysis solution enters your abdominal cavity via a peritoneal catheter.There is more to living than simply not dying. Quality of life means everything. Home dialysis therapy allows people with advanced kidney disease to be independent and to eat and drink more of what they like. They provide comprehensive and compassionate care that will help you live life to the fullest. When provided with comprehensive treatment options education, 50% of new patients choose home dialysis. Quality-of-life surveys consistently support the advantages of home dialysis as compared to in-center hemodialysis.

Full Description: Friedman Research Corporation products are THOR 50m, virtual testing, virtual proving ground, high-value part virtual repair kit, and instant power shelter. They provide support services in aircraft, biomechanics, blast fire, hazmat transport, heavy trucks, manufacturing support, computational design, and vehicle impact. They have developed a suite of virtual testing software systems to support the development, design, and maintenance of safety-related products.
Industry Groups: Government and Military, Hardware, Privacy and Security, Professional Services, Software
